collectionMetadata.name: Distribution of Disability-Adjusted Life Years by Broad Cause Group
collectionMetadata.description:
Data refers to Singapore residents

Source : Estimates from the Singapore Burden of Disease (GBD) Study 2017

Total of 958,204 life years lost due to mortality and ill-health in 2017.

datasetMetadata.name: Distribution of Disability-Adjusted Life Years by Broad Cause Group
datasetMetadata.description:
Data refers to Singapore residents

Source : Global Burden of Disease (GBD) 2019 Study 

Total of 1,047,768 life-years lost due to mortality and ill-health in 2019.

*Next update for data on i) Daily Smoking and ii) Hyperlipidaemia, Hypertension, Diabetes and Obesity will be from i) NPHS 2019 which will be ready in late 2020 and ii) NPHS 2020 which will be ready in 2021 respectively.
